mayor edward i koch has joined the list of 
leona helmsleys detractors calling the hotel queen the wicked 
witch of the west for behavior unbecoming a billionaire 
for a billionaire to be so chintzy distresses people the 
mayor said monday 
the mayor emphasized that his opinion had nothing to do with 
whether she is guilty of tax evasion for which she is being tried 
in federal court 
thats for a jury to decide he said adding its just 
her chintziness its a case involving the wicked witch of the 
west 
koch also commented on the justice system rich people hire 
the best lawyers and therefore they have better defenses he 
said so in that sense there is an inequity but rich people go 
to jail 
mrs helmsley 69 heads a 5 billion real estate and hotel 
empire with her 80yearold husband harry she is accused of 
evading taxes by disguising millions of dollars of renovations at 
their connecticut estate and other personal items as business 
expenses her husband was found mentally incompetent to stand trial 
