chantal the third named storm of the 1989 atlantic hurricane 
season formed earlier monday from the seasons fourth tropical 
depression in the southcentral gulf 
meanwhile in the open atlantic tropical depression no 5 had 
become tropical storm dean by 11 pm edt it had top sustained 
