<TEXT>
price controls and meat rationing ended 
today and poles braced for soaring food prices the bitter cost of 
the governments bold swift push toward a freemarket economy 
also today solidarity leader lech walesa called for opposition 
lawmakers in parliaments lower house or sejm to vote against the 
ruling communist partys nominee for prime minister gen czeslaw 
kiszczak 
