was stranded on the open life raft with her boyfriend nicholas 
abbott after their yacht sank two days into a trip from bermuda to 
greenpoint ny 
abbott 50 jumped from the raft 10 days later and he is 
believed to have drowned according to the us coast guard 
ms culver 48 was in stable condition tuesday at hamiltons 
king edward vii memorial hospital 
